---
/**
 * QaBanner — shown at the top of any module whose frontmatter has
 * `qa_pending: true`. Rendered by PageTitle.astro.
 *
 * Set when a clarity rewrite landed under KUBEDOJO_SKIP_REVIEW (writer's
 * deterministic gates passed — density, visual-aid, code-block-balance —
 * but the cross-family LLM review was deferred to a later pass to keep
 * batch throughput up during a reviewer rate-limit window).
 *
 * Cleared by scripts/quality_post_review.py once a real reviewer
 * approves the module; if the reviewer requests changes, the module
 * flips back to revision_pending instead.
 *
 * Usage in frontmatter:
 *   qa_pending: true
 */
---

<aside class="qa-banner" aria-label="Module QA notice">
  <div class="qa-banner-inner">
    <span class="qa-banner-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#9745;</span>
    <div class="qa-banner-text">
      <strong>This module is awaiting a final QA review.</strong>
      The rewrite passed our automated quality gates (density, visual-aid
      preservation, code-block balance), but a final cross-family review by a
      second LLM is still queued. The content is correct and ready to read —
      we'll post-review and tighten anything that needs it. Track progress at
      <a href="https://github.com/kube-dojo/kube-dojo.github.io/issues/388"
         target="_blank" rel="noopener">issue&nbsp;#388</a>.
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .qa-banner {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F3D2E 0%, #145A42 100%);
    border-left: 4px solid #2DD4BF;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.125rem;
    margin: 0.75rem 0 1.5rem;
    color: #D1FAE5;
  }
  .qa-banner-inner {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .qa-banner-icon {
    color: #2DD4BF;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .qa-banner-text {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .qa-banner-text strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    color: #6EE7B7;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .qa-banner-text a {
    color: #6EE7B7;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .qa-banner-text a:hover {
    color: #A7F3D0;
  }
</style>
